<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Let all those who seek you rejoice and be glad in you;</para>

<para style="q1">let those who love your salvation always say,</para>

<para style="q1">"May God be praised."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />But I am poor and needy;</para>

<para style="q1">hurry to me, God;</para>

<para style="q1">you are my help and you rescue me.</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh, do not delay.</para>
